sequenceDiagram
  participant Factory
  participant Kafka
  participant PMS
  participant gRPC_API as gRPC API
  participant MMS
  participant PostgreSQL
  participant MongoDB

  Factory->>Kafka: Send production event
  Kafka->>PMS: Deliver event (task details)
  PMS->>PostgreSQL: Store structured task data
  PMS->>MongoDB: Store task logs/config
  PMS->>gRPC_API: Notify downstream systems
  gRPC_API->>MMS: Update with event context
  MMS->>MongoDB: Log monitoring data
